1:1: COMMENT 注曰
1:4: STR_LIT "
    斯篇專演「循環」與「明斷」之妙用。
    借《張丘建算經》之「百錢買百雞」題，
    以驗多重迴圈、算術運算，並以多言列印之功也。
"
7:1: HERE_ARE 吾有
7:3: NUMBER_LIT 1
7:4: VAR_TYPE 言
7:6: SAID 曰
7:7: STR_LIT "今有雞翁一，值錢五；雞母一，值錢三；雞雛三，值錢一。"
7:38: PRINT 書之
8:1: HERE_ARE 吾有
8:3: NUMBER_LIT 1
8:4: VAR_TYPE 言
8:6: SAID 曰
8:7: STR_LIT "凡百錢買雞百隻，問雞翁、母、雛各幾何？"
8:31: PRINT 書之
10:1: HERE_IS_A 有
10:2: VAR_TYPE 數
10:3: NUMBER_LIT 100
10:6: NAME_IT 名之曰
10:9: IDENT '百'
11:1: HERE_IS_A 有
11:2: VAR_TYPE 數
11:3: NUMBER_LIT 0
11:5: NAME_IT 名之曰
11:8: IDENT '翁'
13:1: COMMENT 注曰
13:3: STR_LIT " 第一層迴圈：翁至多二十隻 "
14:1: WHILE_TRUE 恆為是
14:5: IF 若
14:6: IDENT '翁'
14:9: EXP_LOGIC >
14:11: NUMBER_LIT 20
14:13: TOPIC 者
14:14: BREAK 乃止
14:16: END 也
16:5: HERE_IS_A 有
16:6: VAR_TYPE 數
16:7: NUMBER_LIT 0
16:9: NAME_IT 名之曰
16:12: IDENT '母'
17:5: COMMENT 注曰
17:7: STR_LIT " 第二層迴圈：母至多三十三隻 "
18:5: WHILE_TRUE 恆為是
18:9: IF 若
18:10: IDENT '母'
18:13: EXP_LOGIC >
18:15: NUMBER_LIT 33
18:18: TOPIC 者
18:19: BREAK 乃止
18:21: END 也
20:9: COMMENT 注曰
20:11: STR_LIT " 雛 = 百 - 翁 - 母 "
21:9: EXP_MATH -
21:10: IDENT '百'
21:13: ->
21:14: IDENT '翁'
21:18: EXP_MATH -
21:19: ITS 其
21:20: ->
21:21: IDENT '母'
21:25: NAME_IT 名之曰
21:28: IDENT '雛'
23:9: COMMENT 注曰
23:11: STR_LIT " 驗證 雛 是否為三之倍數 (雛 % 3 == 0) "
24:9: EXP_MATH /
24:10: IDENT '雛'
24:13: ->
24:14: NUMBER_LIT 3
24:16: EXP_MATH_OP %
24:21: NAME_IT 名之曰
24:24: IDENT '雛餘'
26:9: IF 若
26:10: IDENT '雛餘'
26:14: EXP_LOGIC ==
26:16: NUMBER_LIT 0
26:17: TOPIC 者
27:13: COMMENT 注曰
27:15: STR_LIT " 總價 = 翁*5 + 母*3 + 雛/3 "
28:13: EXP_MATH *
28:14: IDENT '翁'
